repos/dali-ui/wiki/ScrollView.md:334:| `ScrollingSignal` | `void(ScrollView)` | Each frame while scrolling |
repos/dali-ui/wiki/ScrollView.md:335:| `ScrollFinishedSignal` | `void(ScrollView)` | Scrolling ends (drag released or fling completes) |
repos/dali-ui/wiki/ScrollView.md:336:| `DragStartedSignal` | `void(ScrollView)` | Pan threshold crossed, drag begins |
repos/dali-ui/wiki/ScrollView.md:337:| `DraggingSignal` | `void(ScrollView, float deltaX, float deltaY)` | Each pan gesture update while dragging |
repos/dali-ui/wiki/ScrollView.md:338:| `DragFinishedSignal` | `void(ScrollView)` | Pan gesture released |
